          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1719319958272-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the pork is cooking, reboil half a kettle</p><p>Combine your <strong>carrot & cabbage slaw mix </strong>with your <strong>mayo</strong> and the <strong>remaining white wine vinegar</strong></p><p>Add a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>slaw</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1719319962576-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1719319962576-x400.jpg",
