            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the potatoes are tender, drain, return them to the pot</p><p>Add a small knob of <strong>butter</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> to the potatoes and mash them until smooth – this is your <strong>sweet potato mash</strong></p><p>Cover with a lid to keep warm until serving</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1719319982458-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1719319982458-x400.jpg",
