            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1723624486768-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice the <strong>rested pork</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>sliced pork</strong> with the <strong>sweet potato mash </strong>and<strong> slaw </strong>to the side</p><p>Drizzle the <strong>jerk-spiced sauce </strong>over the <strong>sliced pork</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
